

---------------

download lorcon-old:
svn co http://802.11ninja.net/svn/lorcon/branch/lorcon-old lorcon

cd lorcon
./configure --prefix=/usr
make
make install

Download pylorcon (not pylorcon2)
sudo python setup.py install
 - For this step you will need the python headers, on debian try installing 'python-dev' package
 - You will also need 'libpcap-dev' package

repeat for:
 -pcapy
 -pcrypto
 -keyczar
 -pyasn1	(If you have 'python-setuptools' installed just run: 'easy_install pyasn1')
